# project names, editor paths, private UI state, or other contextual details.
docs/references/validation/
docs/references/screenshots/
docs/references/**/*.png
docs/references/**/*.jpg
docs/references/**/*.jpeg
docs/references/**/*.webp
docs/references/**/*.gif

